race.comment: Looks an ideal first Queensland assignment for NOVEMBER AIR (10). NSW form good for this including a fresh-up win and a placing last time at Newcastle. Looks the one to beat on best figures. BURLEIGH MAGIC (4) scored a last stride win here last time over further . Drawn for a soft run and with clear running will be flashing home late this sharper trip. RUN LUCY RUN (8) wasn't disgraced fresh in rover company after a long break. Will strip far fitter and extra trip a plus. Can improve sharply. Same goes for NIGHTCAPPED (9) who was out of the money when resuming from a spell here beaten 3.5 lengths. Strips fitter and can play a big role.
